Thank you for creating a list at The Fridge
===============================================
 
Your Shopping List: 
  <% @list_ingredients.each do |li|%> 
    <%= li.quantity unless li.quantity.blank? %>
    <%= li.measurement unless li.measurement.blank? %>
    <%= li.ingredient.name %>
  <% end %>
 
Your Current Recipes:
<% @recipes.each do |recipe|%> 
  <%= recipe.name %> | <%= recipe.servings %> Servings <%= recipe.source_url %>
<% end %>

